            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "瑞銀將英國股市評級下調至中性,認為上漲空間有限",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/DQLNX.dq7sUdtkl4yFMaFA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/LYNXMPEA9S0AF_M.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Investing.com — 瑞銀已將其對英國股市的展望下調至中性,理由是儘管估值合理且預期盈利增長,但與全球市場相比上漲潛力有限。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">根據瑞銀首席投資辦公室週四發布的最新研究報告,富時100指數目前的遠期市盈率為13.5倍,略高於1990年以來12.8倍的中位數。該行預計英國企業盈利增長在2026年將達到5%,2027年將達到15%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">瑞銀瑞士股份公司首席投資辦公室股票策略師Matthew Gilman表示,今年英國股市主要受三大因素影響:週期性前景改善,全球製造業採購經理人指數達到多年高位;對人工智能驅動的顛覆性變革的擔憂引發從數位板塊向實體板塊的輪動;以及中東局勢緊張加劇能源安全擔憂。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-a64287e3-9ff1-3faf-9012-751cc7173345-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">瑞銀將富時100指數2026年12月的目標設定為10,500點,而截至週二的當前水平為10,320點。該行預計2026年6月的目標為10,300點。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">這家瑞士銀行已調整其歐洲板塊偏好,在近期表現強勁且盈利上調出現早期放緩跡象後,將歐洲銀行板塊下調至中性。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">瑞銀繼續看好歐洲資訊科技、工業和房地產板塊,這些板塊受益於結構性趨勢,包括記憶體需求、電氣化、製造業回流以及國防開支增加。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">在樂觀情境下,瑞銀認為如果全球增長在寬鬆金融環境和信心改善的支持下更快改善,富時100指數到2026年12月有可能達到11,300點。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">大宗商品價格上漲和英鎊走弱也可能提振英國股市,因為富時100指數75%至80%的收入來自英國以外地區。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">然而,該行也概述了下行情境,如果由於中東能源供應持續中斷導致經濟疲軟,可能延遲美國和英國的降息,目標將降至7,200點。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">美歐貿易緊張局勢重現或大宗商品價格下跌也可能拖累表現,因為大宗商品板塊約佔富時100指數盈利的20%至25%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>此文章由人工智能協助翻譯。更多資訊，請參閱我們的使用條款。</em></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%91%9E%E9%8A%80%E5%B0%87%E8%8B%B1%E5%9C%8B%E8%82%A1%E5%B8%82%E8%A9%95%E7%B4%9A%E4%B8%8B%E8%AA%BF%E8%87%B3%E4%B8%AD%E6%80%A7-%E8%AA%8D%E7%82%BA%E4%B8%8A%E6%BC%B2%E7%A9%BA%E9%96%93%E6%9C%89%E9%99%90-134809908.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-03-20 21:52:40",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "立足股壇｜騰訊阿里後市部署｜JK爸爸（陳立展）",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/mHcAzwLEJmyMQtQoRm3rkg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/zh-tw/bossmind_356/eaad463dfa7fed348ae77678da06a339\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">在季度研討會分享的4隻利是股，近日均有不錯表現，當中更有一隻已錄得兩成升幅。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">利是股之一的奇瑞汽車（9973）早在本月初已提及24元水平應得買入，周四除逆市上升外，更漲至29.3元，帳面升幅已超過兩成。不過，現價追入值搏率不高。奇端的基石投資者股份將於下周三解禁，若基石投資者沽貨離場令股價回調，反可視為入市增持的機會。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">另一利是股則網易（9999）可分注買入，首注在182元，另外兩注在160元至170元之間買入。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-43cdbc39-986b-3bdd-8586-a58a81c09b3f-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">投資者較關注的騰訊（700）績後裂後低開，周四跌至513元，已具值搏率。由於騰訊短期跌勢或未喘定，投資者也可考慮部署行使價500元的沽出認沽期權（short put），準備可在更低位接貨。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">阿里（9988）周四收市後公佈業績遜預期，不排除開市後會有沽壓。股價低於130元的阿里已經吸引。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>陳立展（JK爸爸</strong>）<br/><strong>獨立股評人<br/>資深期權投資者</strong></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>註：專欄作家言論不代表本網立場</strong></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%AB%8B%E8%B6%B3%E8%82%A1%E5%A3%87-%E9%A8%B0%E8%A8%8A%E9%98%BF%E9%87%8C%E5%BE%8C%E5%B8%82%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2-jk%E7%88%B8%E7%88%B8-%E9%99%B3%E7%AB%8B%E5%B1%95-131500298.html",
